<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219895>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitus, dorsal view. A – B Weyhia pallidimanu IBSP 3 (A syntype 3, B syntype Ƥ); C Acrogonyleptes cheguevarai IBSP 10607, paratype Ƥ; D – E Hernandaria anitagaribaldiae IBSP 5854 (D non type Ƥ, E paratype 3); F – G Acanthopachyloides patellaris IBSP 10085 (F paratype 3, G paratype Ƥ); H – I Anoplogynus nasutus IBSP 10093 (H syntype 3, I syntype Ƥ). Scale lines: 1 mm: C – E, H – I; 5 mm: A – B, F – G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219896>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitus, dorsal view. A Cercopachylus fragilis IBSP 10096, paratype Ƥ; B Discocyrtulosoma soaresi IBSP 10086, paratype 3; C Discocyrtus pectinifemur IBSP 42, holotype 3; D – E Eusarcus caparaoensis (D holotype 3 IBSP 2904, E paratype Ƥ IBSP 2903); F – G Eusarcus cavernicola (F paratype 3 IBSP 1300, G paratype Ƥ IBSP 1287); H Guaranilia nigrosulcata IBSP 72, holotype 3; I Jacarepaguana pectinifemur IBSP 10104, holotype 3. Scale lines: 1 mm: A – B, D – G, I; 5 mm: C, H." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219897>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Habitus, dorsal view. A Japyra regularis IBSP 7, holotype 3; B Melloleitanius barretensis IBSP 10083, holotype 3; C – D Pachyloides taurus IBSP 78 (C syntype 3, D syntype Ƥ); E Parabristoweia maculipalpi IBSP 10099, holotype 3; F Tabatinguera insignis IBSP 53, paratype 3; G Yraguara annulipes IBSP 63, syntype Ƥ; H Currala luteolimbata IBSP 10092, holotype Ƥ; I Piraquara schubarti IBSP 10084, holotype 3. Scale lines: 1 mm: A, E, G; 5 mm: B – D, F, H – I." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219897/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

